<Title><![CDATA[State Boundaries]]></Title>         <Abstract><![CDATA[This map layer portrays the State boundaries of the United States, and theboundaries of Puerto Rico and the U.S. Virgin Islands. The map layer wascreated by extracting the State boundary polygons from the individual1:2,000,000-scale State boundary Digital Line Graph (DLG) files producedby the U.S. Geological Survey. These files were then merged into a singlecoverage. This is an updated version of the June 2002 map layer; thedate when each State was admitted to the United States was added.]]></Abstract> <CRS>CRS:84</CRS> <CRS>EPSG:4326</CRS> <CRS>EPSG:3785</CRS>
